d over again for years, even for centuries. From this book, the reader will derive the confidence that there are not only answers, but excellent, thought provoking, logical answers to any and all difficulties abut the Faith which may arise. Fr Laux\'s presentation is thus a powerful tool to help souls hold fast with firm confidence to their Faith which time and again has proved to be the bulwark of sanity in this world, as well as the inestimable Pearl of Great Price for which true believers will sacrifice anything to possess.','2009-01-01','https://www.tanbooks.com/index.php/catholic-apologetics-a-course-in-religion-book-iv-2.html',168,'-','5.5\" x 8.5\" x 0.35\"',100,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Apologetics-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-Categor',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-Categor-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-NichEth',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-NichEth-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-PostAn',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-PostAn-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-PriorAn',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arist-PriorAn-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arith1-Saad',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arith1-Saad-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arith2-Saad',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arith2-Saad-Exercises',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','-','1900-01-01','-',0,'-','-',10000,0.00,18.00,0,0),('Arith3-Saad',1,1,'1',20,'0','0','-','